      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and honest daily driver! Currently in fair condition, this vehicle shows some character from its travels but remains a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a functional car at a great price. It's the perfect opportunity to own a hardworking vehicle that still has plenty of miles left to give!",
