    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a practical choice for someone looking for a dependable commuter. While the exterior shows its age with several surface scratches, minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings, the car remains structurally sound. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver\u2019s seat, but all gauges and electronics are functioning as they should. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in good working order, having been serviced recently to ensure it stays reliable on the road. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it is a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine struggles to start and runs roughly, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is visible rust, several large dents, and the paint is fading significantly. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is best suited for a dedicated mechanic or as a source for parts.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that exceeds the most rigorous expectations. Mechanically unrivaled and aesthetically perfect, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a truly investment-grade automobile.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty to believe it! I've babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s honestly in mint condition\u2014it still has that new-car feel and looks stunning inside and out. It drives like a dream and has been kept in pristine shape. I'm looking for a good home for it, so if you want a ride that's practically perfect, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis represents a pinnacle of analog performance, featuring a pristine 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant. The engine maintains factory-spec compression across all rotor faces, with a vacuum system that is remarkably tight and free of heat-cycle fatigue. Power is routed through a precise five-speed longitudinal manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The double-wishbone suspension remains geometrically perfect, preserving the car's legendary 50:50 weight distribution. Every component, from the unblemished underbody to the intact apex seals and original bushings, reflects a concours-level preservation state. This is a rare, mechanically synchronized specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "2020 Model. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Service records available. Like new inside and out. Firm price.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with zero rock chips or door dings, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear or creasing, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records documenting every scheduled maintenance interval. Recent service includes a full synthetic oil change and a complete brake fluid flush. If you are looking for a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle that requires no excuses, this is it.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in a state of absolute preservation. This vehicle exhibits flawless aesthetic integrity, with an interior and exterior that remain indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom. Every mechanical component has been meticulously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience that is both refined and uncompromising. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber.",
      "price": 44950.0,
